  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Investing the Timed Up and Go (TUG) Test in Hemiplegic Patients Using 3D Motion Analysis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The timed up and go is a routine quick test assessing motor functional tasks including stand
      up ,walk 3 m,turn around and sitting down.We will included hemiplegic patients to quantify
      biomechanic parameters
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
